---
import LogoMark from './LogoMark.astro';
---
<section class="sec" id="opensource"><div class="wrap">
  <div class="os">
    <div>
      <span class="kick">Open source</span>
      <h2 class="sectitle" style="margin:8px 0 6px">Free, and actually yours</h2>
      <div class="oslist">
        <div class="osrow"><span class="t">✓</span><span><b>GPL-3.0.</b> Read it, build it, fork it. No telemetry, no account required to record.</span></div>
        <div class="osrow"><span class="t">✓</span><span><b>Local-first.</b> Clips live on your disk. Nothing uploads unless you press upload.</span></div>
        <div class="osrow"><span class="t">✓</span><span><b>Built in the open.</b> Beta and moving fast — issues and roadmap are public; self-updating so fixes reach you quickly.</span></div>
        <div class="osrow"><span class="t">✓</span><span><b>Signed builds incoming</b> via the SignPath Foundation — beta builds are unsigned for now.</span></div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top:20px;display:flex;gap:12px"><a class="btn ghost" href="https://github.com/gankedtv/rewynd">★ Star on GitHub</a><a class="btn line" href="https://github.com/gankedtv/rewynd#readme">Read the docs</a></div>
    </div>
    <div class="repo">
      <div class="top"><LogoMark style="width:18px;height:18px" /><b>gankedtv / rewynd</b><span style="margin-left:auto;color:var(--ts)">GPL-3.0 · beta</span></div>
      <div class="body">
        <div class="ln"><span class="k">$</span> curl -fsSL https://rewynd.gg/install.sh | sh</div>
        <div class="ln" style="color:var(--ts)">↳ fetching latest AppImage…</div>
        <div class="ln"><span class="k">✓</span> rewynd installed · run <span style="color:var(--tp)">rewynd</span> to start</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div></section>
